the craziest of the crazies.

13:57.236 --> 13:58.803
Someone named "Warri0r-p0se"

13:58.847 --> 14:00.631
posted some pretty
outrageous statements.

14:00.674 --> 14:03.112
"Hoyt will never touch
another young girl."

14:03.155 --> 14:05.636
And he posted one
this morning too at 11:12 a.m.

14:05.679 --> 14:08.682
an hour after the murder.

14:08.726 --> 14:10.641
"Hoyt is no longer a problem.

14:10.684 --> 14:12.338
God bless America."

14:12.382 --> 14:14.253
- Run down the IP address
right away.

14:14.297 --> 14:15.951
- I already did.
Post was sent from a café

14:15.994 --> 14:18.040
in Brooklyn called
Coffee and Smile.

14:18.083 --> 14:20.433
- Oh.
- Mm.

14:20.477 --> 14:22.348
- Why has it become mandatory
for coffee shops

14:22.392 --> 14:24.133
to be called stupid names?

14:24.176 --> 14:26.004
- That's why I drink tea.

14:26.048 --> 14:28.093
Talk to the manager.
See if they have video,

14:28.137 --> 14:30.313
and see if you can find out
who sent those posts.

14:30.356 --> 14:32.184
- All right.
- You got it.

14:32.228 --> 14:35.361
[motor running]

14:38.060 --> 14:39.452
Hey.

14:39.496 --> 14:41.454
Manny Lopez!
- Yeah?

14:41.498 --> 14:43.630
- Yeah, we need to talk.

14:43.674 --> 14:45.676
- About what?
- Is that you drinking coffee

14:45.719 --> 14:47.983
at a place
called Coffee and Smile?

14:48.026 --> 14:49.985
- Is that a crime?
- Uh, no, not yet.

14:50.028 --> 14:52.117
But the way things are going,
who knows?

14:52.161 --> 14:54.511
Might be considered racist
someday soon.

14:54.554 --> 14:56.556
- It's only a matter of time,
huh?

14:56.600 --> 14:57.862
- Well, there is a crime

14:57.906 --> 15:01.344
against pushing someone
in front of a bus.

15:01.387 --> 15:03.172
That's why we're really here.

15:03.215 --> 15:04.738
Come on.

15:04.782 --> 15:07.002
Let's take a ride down
to the precinct.

15:08.177 --> 15:09.091
[door shuts]

15:11.876 --> 15:14.096
- Manny, we, uh--
we analyzed your emails

15:14.139 --> 15:16.968
and your chat history.

15:17.012 --> 15:19.362
You weren't the biggest fan
of Derek Hoyt.

15:19.405 --> 15:22.843
- Don't worry, bro.
There's more.

15:22.887 --> 15:27.022
We found video of you near the
intersection of 29th and 10th

15:27.065 --> 15:29.676
right around the time
Hoyt was murdered.

15:29.720 --> 15:31.765
Look at you, plain as day,

15:31.809 --> 15:33.724
one block from the crime scene

15:33.767 --> 15:37.423
about 65 seconds
before Hoyt was killed.

15:37.467 --> 15:39.338
[gasps sarcastically]

15:39.382 --> 15:42.080
There you are again,
walking east on 29th Street

15:42.124 --> 15:47.781
right behind Hoyt about
35 seconds before he was pushed.

15:47.825 --> 15:49.392
- You want to get ahead of this,

15:49.435 --> 15:51.350
tell us your side of the story?

15:51.394 --> 15:57.791
♪

15:57.835 --> 16:00.620
- Derek Hoyt was a senior
member of the liberal,

16:00.664 --> 16:05.582
sex-crazed cabal
that is destroying our country.

16:05.625 --> 16:07.410
He planned to kidnap
a young kid!

16:07.453 --> 16:10.021
♪

16:10.065 --> 16:11.370
- So you killed him?

16:11.414 --> 16:13.024
- Damn right!

16:13.068 --> 16:14.417
I love this country.

16:14.460 --> 16:16.158
So I did what I had to do.

16:16.201 --> 16:19.248
- Yeah, you sure did.
Now you gotta pay the tab, bro.

16:19.291 --> 16:20.771
- What does that mean?

16:20.814 --> 16:22.903
- It means you're under arrest
for murder.

16:22.947 --> 16:24.644
- Hold on, big fella!
Hold on.

16:31.695 --> 16:31.869
.

16:31.912 --> 16:34.089
- The People ask for remand,
Your Honor.

16:34.132 --> 16:35.307
We believe the defendant
is a flight risk,

16:35.351 --> 16:36.874
given the potential
penalty he's facing.

16:36.917 --> 16:39.050
- Mr. Lopez has no priors,

16:39.094 --> 16:41.139
has substantial ties
to New York.

16:41.183 --> 16:43.098
- Bail is set at $2 million.

16:43.141 --> 16:44.577
- That's prohibitive.

16:44.621 --> 16:46.971
Mr. Lopez doesn't have access
to that kind of money.

16:47.015 --> 16:49.191
- I'm not so sure about that.
- Excuse me?

16:49.234 --> 16:50.801
- My clerk informed me
that apparently

16:50.844 --> 16:52.063
some self-proclaimed patriot

16:52.107 --> 16:55.110
started a GoFundMe page
for Mr. Lopez.

16:55.153 --> 16:57.286
Already raised $900,000.

16:57.329 --> 16:59.244
Bail is set at $2 million.

16:59.288 --> 17:01.681
[gavel knocks]
Next case.

17:03.683 --> 17:05.163
[knocks on door]

17:05.207 --> 17:06.904
- Been reviewing
the most recent posts

17:06.947 --> 17:09.646
in Manny's favorite chat room,
Rogue Wave.

17:09.689 --> 17:10.951
There's lots of crazy chatter

17:10.995 --> 17:13.084
about Hoyt trafficking
young kids,

17:13.128 --> 17:16.131
straight out
of the QAnon playbook.

17:16.174 --> 17:19.395
"Credible intel says Hoyt
is abducting young children,

17:19.438 --> 17:20.744
"selling them
to sex-traffickers

17:20.787 --> 17:22.180
in Washington, DC."

17:22.224 --> 17:24.922
The next day, which is
the actual day of the murder,

17:24.965 --> 17:26.576
the same person sent this:

17:26.619 --> 17:29.274
"FBI contact says
Hoyt is carrying out

17:29.318 --> 17:30.884
"a kidnapping plot tonight.

17:30.928 --> 17:34.105
Unfortunately, feds don't have
enough evidence to arrest."

17:34.149 --> 17:37.152
Right after that,
the same person sent this:

17:37.195 --> 17:40.764
"Who out there is brave enough
to take action and protect

17:40.807 --> 17:44.289
our great country from
the corrupt liberal cabal?"

17:44.333 --> 17:48.119
- So this poster is just
inventing inflammatory lies,

17:48.163 --> 17:49.773
hoping to rile up the masses?

17:49.816 --> 17:51.775
- It was even more targeted
than that.

17:51.818 --> 17:53.864
He knew his audience.

17:53.907 --> 17:56.040
He was looking to rile up
the specific people

17:56.084 --> 17:58.260
who already believe
these ridiculous lies.

17:58.303 --> 17:59.696
- We know who this person is?

17:59.739 --> 18:01.219
- No,
email address is encrypted,

18:01.263 --> 18:03.482
but he's definitely
the ringleader.

18:03.526 --> 18:07.182
He's the one who posted
the phony pedophile photos too.

18:08.270 --> 18:12.317
- So if Manny actually believed
what this poster was saying,

18:12.361 --> 18:15.712
killing Hoyt to thwart
the alleged kidnapping

18:15.755 --> 18:18.671
actually makes some sense.

18:18.715 --> 18:20.325
I mean, even though it's crazy.

18:20.369 --> 18:22.936
- Good chance Manny's going
to claim justification--

18:22.980 --> 18:25.025
thought Hoyt was going
to kidnap a young girl,

18:25.069 --> 18:27.898
so he kills Hoyt
to save the young girl.

18:27.941 --> 18:29.378
- Even though there
really wasn't a young girl

18:29.421 --> 18:32.032
in harm's way.
- Exactly.

18:32.076 --> 18:34.905
- That's obviously a stretch,
but

18:34.948 --> 18:36.559
it'll give Manny's lawyer
a chance

18:36.602 --> 18:38.561
to talk about
the liberal lunatics,

18:38.604 --> 18:40.389
the alleged
sex trafficking ring--

18:40.432 --> 18:41.955
- Make it about politics,
not law.

18:41.999 --> 18:45.568
- Which means
anything is possible.

18:45.611 --> 18:47.526
Call Cosgrove and Bernard.

18:47.570 --> 18:50.790
Have them talk to HTAU
and track down the IP address

18:50.834 --> 18:52.444
of this ringleader.

18:52.488 --> 18:54.054
We need to figure out

18:54.098 --> 18:56.796
why he was so invested
in destroying Hoyt,

18:56.840 --> 18:59.669
and if he's connected
to this murder.

18:59.712 --> 19:00.800
- On it.

19:00.844 --> 19:03.673
♪

19:03.716 --> 19:05.196
- Sorry, guys.
We're recording.

19:08.895 --> 19:11.333
- Kennel of troglodytes.
The U.S. government has...

19:11.376 --> 19:12.769
- Reed.
- Literally--

19:12.812 --> 19:14.031
- We need to talk.

19:14.074 --> 19:16.207
- What is goin' on?
Wha--

19:16.251 --> 19:21.778
♪

19:21.821 --> 19:23.432
Ladies and gentlemen,

19:23.475 --> 19:26.435
two policemen have just entered
my studio.

19:26.478 --> 19:29.612
My guess is, the liberal mafia
gave 'em a call,

19:29.655 --> 19:30.787
told 'em to come on down here,

19:30.830 --> 19:32.223
and stomp on
my First Amendment rights,

19:32.267 --> 19:33.964
and that's how it is
these days, right?

19:34.007 --> 19:35.444
You don't like what
a true patriot is saying,

19:35.487 --> 19:37.359
you take away their voice.
You stomp on their rights

19:37.402 --> 19:40.492
to say what they believe,
or better yet,

19:40.536 --> 19:42.059
you send the police after 'em.

19:42.102 --> 19:44.322
- Get off the damn mic, man.
We have business to discuss.

19:44.366 --> 19:45.671
- You have a warrant?

19:45.715 --> 19:47.325
- We'd just like to ask you
a few questions.

19:47.369 --> 19:49.806
- I'm not saying a damn word.
Get the hell out of my studio.

19:49.849 --> 19:51.373
- Watch yourself, Reed.

19:51.416 --> 19:56.029
- Oh, the, uh, Black detective
is now threatening me.

19:56.073 --> 19:58.510
- Why did you post those
crazy lies about Derek Hoyt?

19:58.554 --> 19:59.555
- Get out!
- Hmm?

19:59.598 --> 20:01.296
- Now!
- Why did you post--

20:01.339 --> 20:02.514
- Detective,
I'm not saying it again.

20:02.558 --> 20:05.909
You heard me, Detective!
Get out!

20:05.952 --> 20:08.216
- Kev, it's not worth it.

20:08.259 --> 20:10.435
♪

20:10.479 --> 20:11.480
- [chuckles]

20:11.523 --> 20:14.831
♪

20:14.874 --> 20:17.137
- You think Jordan Reed
was an accomplice?

20:17.181 --> 20:19.749
- Oh, he stirred him up,
that's for sure.

20:19.792 --> 20:21.925
He posted all kind
of outrageous lies

20:21.968 --> 20:25.320
and made Hoyt into a pedophile,
but there's more.

20:25.363 --> 20:29.193
Reed began to communicate
directly with the defendant.

20:29.237 --> 20:31.282
- We found lots of phone calls
between the two of them

20:31.326 --> 20:33.763
on the day prior to
and on the day of the murder.

20:33.806 --> 20:37.245
- Any legitimate reason for
these two to be communicating?

20:37.288 --> 20:41.161
- Reed is an Ivy League elitist
who grew up on 5th Avenue,

20:41.205 --> 20:43.816
Manny's a day laborer
from Staten Island.

20:43.860 --> 20:44.948
- You think
they were discussing

20:44.991 --> 20:48.256
Hoyt's imminent demise?

20:48.299 --> 20:50.301
Wanna trade up,

20:50.345 --> 20:51.868
hold Reed accountable?

20:56.176 --> 20:57.830
Okay.

20:57.874 --> 20:58.962
Talk to the defendant.

20:59.005 --> 21:01.225
See if he'll cooperate.

21:04.402 --> 21:08.363
- We know you pushed Derek Hoyt
in front of that bus.

21:08.406 --> 21:12.454
Good news, for you,
is we think Jordan Reed

21:12.497 --> 21:14.020
is really the one responsible.

21:14.064 --> 21:16.066
- We're happy to cooperate

21:16.109 --> 21:19.374
if you can reduce
the charge to Man One.

21:19.417 --> 21:20.462
- No promises.

21:20.505 --> 21:21.985
We'll listen to what
he has to say.

21:22.028 --> 21:24.117
Come back with a deal
in writing.

21:24.161 --> 21:26.729
- Just answer their questions,
Manny, and nothing you say

21:26.772 --> 21:29.122
can be used against you.

21:29.166 --> 21:31.908
- You and Reed talked
on the phone several times

21:31.951 --> 21:33.562
before and after the murder.

21:33.605 --> 21:35.041
What did you two discuss?

21:35.085 --> 21:37.261
- We talked about
a lot of things.

21:37.305 --> 21:38.741
The country,

21:38.784 --> 21:41.352
the left-wing fascists
trying to take over the country.

21:41.396 --> 21:44.399
- Did Reed talk to you
about killing Derek Hoyt?

21:44.442 --> 21:46.052
- Reed's a good guy.

21:46.096 --> 21:47.532
He's a straight shooter.

21:47.576 --> 21:49.491
- No, he's a liar and a fraud.

21:49.534 --> 21:51.536
He was playing you, Manny.

21:51.580 --> 21:53.277
Hoyt wasn't a pedophile.

21:53.321 --> 21:57.063
He was a law-abiding family man
who wanted to run for Congress.

21:57.107 --> 21:59.065
- Sure, that's what
the liberal media says.

21:59.109 --> 22:00.632
- No, that's what the facts say.

22:00.676 --> 22:03.113
- Reed is using you
and your chat room friends

22:03.156 --> 22:04.593
to become a billionaire.

22:04.636 --> 22:06.159
- For God sakes, Manny.

22:06.203 --> 22:09.598
You worry about you, not Reed.

22:09.641 --> 22:12.340
Now, you tell them
what you two talked about.

22:16.300 --> 22:18.650
- He said Hoyt
was very dangerous,

22:18.694 --> 22:20.130
a threat to the country,

22:20.173 --> 22:22.437
that the wave was coming,
and that he needed people

22:22.480 --> 22:25.309
to neutralize
that left-wing threat,

22:25.353 --> 22:29.879
people willing to take bold
and decisive action.

22:29.922 --> 22:31.315
- Did he ask you to kill him?

22:31.359 --> 22:33.796
- He kept using the word
"neutralize,"

22:33.839 --> 22:36.320
but I knew what he meant.

22:36.364 --> 22:38.627
- Did you expect anything
in return for killing Hoyt--

22:38.670 --> 22:41.194
money, a car?

22:41.238 --> 22:44.937
- He said that his company
rewards true patriots,

22:44.981 --> 22:49.464
those willing to take action,
that kind of thing, you know?

22:49.507 --> 22:53.468
♪

22:54.817 --> 22:55.208
.

22:55.252 --> 22:57.776
- Docket number CR 54378-22,

22:57.820 --> 23:01.780
People versus Jordan Reed,
Murder in the First Degree.

23:01.824 --> 23:03.521
- How does the defendant plead?

23:03.565 --> 23:05.915
- Not guilty, Your Honor.

23:05.958 --> 23:07.917
- People on bail?
- Remand.

23:07.960 --> 23:09.266
The defendant is a flight risk.

23:09.309 --> 23:11.050
He has access to private jets,

23:11.094 --> 23:12.269
foreign political leaders--

23:12.312 --> 23:14.271
- This is preposterous,
Your Honor.

23:14.314 --> 23:16.012
My client has done
nothing wrong.

23:16.055 --> 23:17.622
He's committed no crime.

23:17.666 --> 23:19.015
Not his fault some lunatic

23:19.058 --> 23:21.670
pushed Derek Hoyt
in front of a bus.

23:21.713 --> 23:23.976
- Bail is set at $1 million.

23:24.020 --> 23:25.587
Next case.
[gavel knocks]

23:27.327 --> 23:29.112
all chanting:
Free Jordan Reed!

23:29.155 --> 23:32.115
Free Jordan Reed!
Free Jordan Reed!

23:32.158 --> 23:34.422
- So much
for the home field advantage.

23:34.465 --> 23:36.467
- Reed definitely
has a hardcore following.

23:36.511 --> 23:38.295
- That's why we're here
in the first place.

23:38.338 --> 23:39.775
all chanting:
Free Jordan Reed!

23:39.818 --> 23:42.386
♪

23:42.430 --> 23:47.435
- Derek Hoyt was a kind,
decent husband and father.

23:47.478 --> 23:49.654
He was also
an aspiring politician

23:49.698 --> 23:52.483
with a bright future.

23:52.527 --> 23:55.660
So in search of
salacious headlines,

23:55.704 --> 23:58.141
the defendant created
a false narrative

23:58.184 --> 24:00.230
that Derek Hoyt
was a pedophile--

24:00.273 --> 24:03.625
that he was part of a depraved
sex-trafficking ring

24:03.668 --> 24:06.497
that preyed
on underage children.

24:06.541 --> 24:10.632
To help perpetuate
this disgraceful fiction,

24:10.675 --> 24:13.983
he disseminated fake photos
of Derek Hoyt

24:14.026 --> 24:15.680
and young girls on the internet.

24:19.510 --> 24:20.990
You see,

24:21.033 --> 24:23.514
inventing mythical enemies

24:23.558 --> 24:27.344
is a part of
the defendant's business model.

24:27.387 --> 24:29.215
He creates clickbait.

24:29.259 --> 24:32.131
He provides exciting
liberal enemies

24:32.175 --> 24:33.785
for his followers to hate.

24:33.829 --> 24:36.875
He then posts about
these dangerous fascists

24:36.919 --> 24:39.182
and anti-Americans
on his websites,

24:39.225 --> 24:41.097
talks about them
on his streaming platforms

24:41.140 --> 24:44.361
and podcasts,
but the only thing

24:44.404 --> 24:49.192
he really cares about
is money.

24:49.235 --> 24:52.761
Monetizing
the outrage and venom.

24:52.804 --> 24:53.805
That's how the defendant built

24:53.849 --> 24:56.808
his billion dollar
media empire.

24:56.852 --> 25:00.899
In simplest terms,
the defendant made Derek Hoyt

25:00.943 --> 25:03.249
an enemy of the far-right,

25:03.293 --> 25:05.295
then offered Manny Lopez

25:05.338 --> 25:08.559
a misguided, but intelligent
patriotic ex-marine

25:08.603 --> 25:12.084
a financial reward
to kill that enemy,

25:12.128 --> 25:14.391
and Manny Lopez did.

25:14.434 --> 25:17.612
He pushed him
in front of a bus.

25:17.655 --> 25:24.575
♪

25:29.014 --> 25:31.277
Tomorrow, you'll hear
from Mr. Lopez himself.

25:31.321 --> 25:35.107
He will describe this
murder-for-hire arrangement

25:35.151 --> 25:37.545
in more detail
and make it clear

25:37.588 --> 25:41.940
the defendant
should be held accountable

25:41.984 --> 25:43.899
for Mr. Hoyt's death.

25:43.942 --> 25:49.731
♪

25:49.774 --> 25:51.733
- [sighs]

25:51.776 --> 25:53.517
Sometimes,

25:53.561 --> 25:57.434
murder trials
can be complicated.

25:57.477 --> 26:00.655
Now, sometimes, there's--
there's lots of science,

26:00.698 --> 26:04.310
blood evidence,
contradictory testimony.

26:05.529 --> 26:09.446
But sometimes, they're easy.

26:09.489 --> 26:13.537
The answer is sittin' there
right in front of you.

26:13.581 --> 26:18.411
It's so simple and clear,
it's almost confusing.

26:18.455 --> 26:20.718
This is one of those cases.

26:20.762 --> 26:26.202
Manny Lopez pushed Derek Hoyt
in front of a bus.

26:26.245 --> 26:27.943
Jordan Reed didn't.

26:27.986 --> 26:31.207
To hold him guilty for
another man's act of violence

26:31.250 --> 26:34.210
is contrary
to the intent of the law,

26:34.253 --> 26:36.647
and a dangerous attempt
to criminalize

26:36.691 --> 26:39.781
the expression of free speech.

26:39.824 --> 26:43.436
If I say the coach of the
New York Jets is terrible--

26:43.480 --> 26:44.960
[chuckling]
Right? I mean he's an idiot--

26:45.003 --> 26:47.484
he deserves to die.

26:47.527 --> 26:50.966
And the next day,
some lunatic kills him,

26:51.009 --> 26:53.708
pushes him in front of a bus,
for example.

26:53.751 --> 26:59.670
Am I responsible for what this
deranged football fan did?

26:59.714 --> 27:02.499
No, of course not.

27:02.542 --> 27:06.982
Manny Lopez killed Derek Hoyt.

27:07.025 --> 27:09.549
Jordan Reed did not.

27:11.856 --> 27:13.510
Like I said,

27:13.553 --> 27:16.382
sometimes, cases are easy.

27:19.385 --> 27:21.170
- Okay, we're adjourned.

27:21.213 --> 27:22.475
[gavel knocks]

27:24.216 --> 27:27.872
[cell phones vibrating]

27:27.916 --> 27:30.832
♪

27:30.875 --> 27:31.920
- Notify the judge.

27:31.963 --> 27:34.009
I'll--I'll head down
to the hospital.

27:34.052 --> 27:40.450
♪

27:40.493 --> 27:43.409
[indistinct PA announcement]

27:43.453 --> 27:48.937
♪

27:48.980 --> 27:51.853
Excuse me,
I'm looking for Manuel Lopez.

27:51.896 --> 27:54.072
I was told
he was just rushed to the ER.

27:54.116 --> 27:56.553
- And you are?
- Assistant District Attorney

27:56.596 --> 27:58.033
Nolan Price.
Manny's supposed to be

27:58.076 --> 28:00.818
testifying in a murder trial
tomorrow morning.

28:00.862 --> 28:03.125
- Well, I'm afraid
that's not possible.

28:03.168 --> 28:04.779
He's dead.

28:04.822 --> 28:06.258
- He's dead?

28:06.302 --> 28:08.739
- He hanged himself earlier
this morning in his cell.

28:08.783 --> 28:10.915
We tried to revive him, but
there was nothing we could do.

28:10.959 --> 28:17.922
♪

28:20.838 --> 28:21.230
.

28:21.273 --> 28:23.232
- Your Honor, the People's case
was predicated

28:23.275 --> 28:25.713
on Manny Lopez's testimony.

28:25.756 --> 28:28.106
He was, in effect,
the only piece of evidence

28:28.150 --> 28:30.630
that could establish
that Mr. Reed hired him

28:30.674 --> 28:31.719
to kill the victim.

28:31.762 --> 28:33.155
So without Manny,

28:33.198 --> 28:36.027
it's literally impossible
to prove murder-for-hire.

28:36.071 --> 28:38.334
No Manny, no case.
Simple as that.

28:38.377 --> 28:41.076
- Mr. Price, that true?

28:41.119 --> 28:43.992
Is Mr. Lopez
the only ace up your sleeve?

28:44.035 --> 28:46.081
Do you have anything else that
gives you a puncher's chance

28:46.124 --> 28:48.474
to prove your case?
- Not at the moment.

28:48.518 --> 28:50.433
- Then I'm going to grant
the motion to dismiss.

28:50.476 --> 28:52.000
- I have no objection
to dismissing

28:52.043 --> 28:54.002
the murder-for-hire charge.

28:54.045 --> 28:56.569
But we'd still like to proceed

28:56.613 --> 28:59.137
with the lesser-included
offense, Murder Two.

28:59.181 --> 29:00.443
- Under what theory?

29:00.486 --> 29:02.314
- Your client showed
a depraved indifference

29:02.358 --> 29:04.447
to human life.
- Oh, this is ridiculous.

29:04.490 --> 29:08.756
- Reed's lies, his posts,
and photos incited Manny Lopez

29:08.799 --> 29:09.800
to commit murder.

29:09.844 --> 29:12.629
He knew,
or should have known,

29:12.672 --> 29:14.892
that his repeated fabrications
would likely cause

29:14.936 --> 29:17.677
one of his ardent followers
to kill Derek Hoyt.

29:17.721 --> 29:20.680
- Is this a joke?
You wanna try Reed for murder

29:20.724 --> 29:23.509
based on a series
of stupid chat room posts?

29:23.553 --> 29:24.641
- That's exactly what
I wanna do.

29:24.684 --> 29:25.773
- Chat room posts,

29:25.816 --> 29:27.731
social media rants,
they're protected

29:27.775 --> 29:29.254
under the First Amendment.

29:29.298 --> 29:31.430
Jordan Reed can say
whatever the hell he wants.

29:31.474 --> 29:33.519
He could talk about
liberal cannibals

29:33.563 --> 29:36.087
and underage sex trafficking
rings all day long.

29:36.131 --> 29:39.003
- Your client yelled "fire"
in a crowded movie theater,

29:39.047 --> 29:42.528
and Derek Hoyt
got trampled to death.

29:42.572 --> 29:45.531
We have every right
to move forward on Murder Two.

29:47.316 --> 29:50.406
- I agree with Mr. Price.
There's a case here.

29:50.449 --> 29:53.583
I'm not sure if it's winnable,
but it's certainly triable.

29:53.626 --> 29:55.803
So let's do it.

29:55.846 --> 30:01.634
♪

30:01.678 --> 30:03.288
- When the photos
were enlarged,

30:03.332 --> 30:06.378
significant pixelation
and discoloring were evident--

30:06.422 --> 30:08.554
two telltale signs
of alteration.

30:08.598 --> 30:10.382
- So they're fake?
They were photoshopped?

30:10.426 --> 30:12.602
- Yes, the images
from the young girls'

30:12.645 --> 30:16.475
legitimate social accounts were
copied and then transposed

30:16.519 --> 30:19.348
onto photos with Derek Hoyt
and vice-versa.

30:19.391 --> 30:22.873
- These fake photos were posted
to a virtual community

30:22.917 --> 30:25.397
called Rogue Wave,
a place where believers

30:25.441 --> 30:27.878
in the so-called
QAnon conspiracy theory

30:27.922 --> 30:30.315
gather to share ideas.

30:30.359 --> 30:31.577
Were you able to determine

30:31.621 --> 30:33.623
which IP address
they were sent from?

30:33.666 --> 30:38.933
- Yes.
IP address 198.51.100.0/24.

30:39.672 --> 30:42.893
- These statements were
also posted to Rogue Wave.

30:42.937 --> 30:45.026
Do you know which IP address
they came from?

30:45.069 --> 30:46.505
- Yes, same one.

30:46.549 --> 30:49.247
- And were you able to trace
that IP address

30:49.291 --> 30:51.597
to a particular office?
- Yes.

30:51.641 --> 30:53.991
It was located
in a large corner office

30:54.035 --> 30:56.951
in a company called Audix, LLC.

30:56.994 --> 31:01.085
The nameplate on the door said,
"Jordan Reed."

31:01.129 --> 31:02.304
- Nothing further.

31:07.918 --> 31:10.399
- You have no proof Mr. Reed

31:10.442 --> 31:13.750
actually created those photos,
correct?

31:13.793 --> 31:15.883
- No, but they were sent
from his computer.

31:15.926 --> 31:20.539
- You also have no proof
Mr. Reed wrote or posted

31:20.583 --> 31:23.629
those statements to Rogue Wave?

31:23.673 --> 31:27.982
- I don't, but they were sent
from his computer.

31:28.025 --> 31:29.157
- Nothing further.

31:31.550 --> 31:33.813
- We have the posts
and the photos.

31:33.857 --> 31:36.816
It's not perfect,
but it'll show that Reed

31:36.860 --> 31:39.167
wanted to incite action--

31:39.210 --> 31:41.386
no, that his objective

31:41.430 --> 31:43.911
was to prompt
his most zealous followers

31:43.954 --> 31:47.566
to commit an act of violence
against Derek Hoyt.

31:47.610 --> 31:50.265
- It's a good start,
but we need more

31:50.308 --> 31:52.832
to bolster our theory
of depraved indifference.

31:52.876 --> 31:56.575
We need to show Reed knew
there was a strong likelihood

31:56.619 --> 31:59.317
Manny would kill Hoyt
based on his outrageous posts

31:59.361 --> 32:00.840
and only those
outrageous posts.

32:00.884 --> 32:03.887
- We have what we have.
I mean, it'd be great

32:03.931 --> 32:05.454
if I had a beach house
in South Hampton,

32:05.497 --> 32:06.803
but I don't, so I make do

32:06.846 --> 32:08.936
with my cousin's cottage
on the Jersey Shore

32:08.979 --> 32:11.025
for three days in August.

32:11.068 --> 32:14.593
- We're asking the jury
to convict someone for murder,

32:14.637 --> 32:16.987
for spreading lies
on the internet.

32:17.031 --> 32:18.989
This could be ground-breaking,

32:19.033 --> 32:20.599
like convicting
Trump for the murders

32:20.643 --> 32:23.167
that took place on January 6th.

32:23.211 --> 32:25.213
We need to give the jury more.

32:27.693 --> 32:30.218
- We know Manny attended
three recent rallies

32:30.261 --> 32:32.220
where Reed
was the featured speaker.

32:32.263 --> 32:34.918
So let's start there.

32:36.354 --> 32:38.008
♪

32:38.052 --> 32:40.489
- Is that you standing beside
Jordan Reed?

32:40.532 --> 32:42.099
- Yeah, that's me.

32:42.143 --> 32:43.318
- What'd you two talk about?

32:43.361 --> 32:45.059
- Nothing too specific.

32:45.102 --> 32:47.757
- Did he ever mention
a guy named Derek Hoyt?

32:47.800 --> 32:49.019
- No, Who's he?

32:49.063 --> 32:50.890
- He got murdered a while ago.

32:50.934 --> 32:53.197
The guy you're standing next
to, Manny Lopez, pushed him

32:53.241 --> 32:56.200
in front of a bus.
- Damn.

32:56.244 --> 32:58.115
That's crazy.
- Did Manny say anything

32:58.159 --> 33:01.205
to Reed that might suggest
he'd do something violent?

33:01.249 --> 33:03.207
- No, he barely talked.

33:03.251 --> 33:04.426
- Did you guys
talk about anything

33:04.469 --> 33:06.515
other than
how screwed up the country is?

33:06.558 --> 33:09.039
- Yeah, lots of stuff.

33:09.083 --> 33:10.084
- Like what?

33:10.127 --> 33:11.694
- Uh, the Knicks.

33:11.737 --> 33:14.262
Me and Reed were pissed about
Kemba Walker being benched.

33:16.481 --> 33:18.048
- They didn't talk
about Derek Hoyt

33:18.092 --> 33:19.571
or committing acts of violence?

33:19.615 --> 33:20.964
It was just a pleasant chat

33:21.008 --> 33:23.836
about life in America,
circa 2022?

33:23.880 --> 33:25.621
- According to Pond,
they talked about

33:25.664 --> 33:30.017
everything but Hoyt
or committing acts of violence.

33:30.060 --> 33:31.496
- This is bad.

33:31.540 --> 33:33.411
- It's exculpatory too.

33:33.455 --> 33:34.978
- I'm not so sure.

33:35.022 --> 33:37.372
- It contradicts our entire
thesis that Reed was baiting

33:37.415 --> 33:38.764
his followers to attack Hoyt.

33:38.808 --> 33:40.462
- This is just one conversation,

33:40.505 --> 33:43.030
one simple sound bite--
- A simple sound bite

33:43.073 --> 33:46.424
that favors the defendant.

33:46.468 --> 33:48.078
- [sighs]
You're right.

33:48.122 --> 33:50.254
♪

33:50.298 --> 33:54.432
We need to notify defense.
Let them know what we found,

33:54.476 --> 33:57.435
and then we need
to get back to work,

33:57.479 --> 33:59.829
and figure out
how to win this damn case.

33:59.872 --> 34:04.529
♪

34:06.227 --> 34:06.444
.

34:06.488 --> 34:08.707
- Did you attend
a political rally

34:08.751 --> 34:11.145
at a restaurant called
The Grey Lion on March 10th?

34:11.188 --> 34:14.496
- Yes.
- At this event,

34:14.539 --> 34:18.021
did you happen to have
a conversation with Jordan Reed

34:18.065 --> 34:20.023
and Manny Lopez?
- I did.

34:20.067 --> 34:22.417
- What did you three discuss?

34:22.460 --> 34:24.941
- We talked about how
screwed up our country is.

34:24.984 --> 34:26.943
- Can you be more specific?

34:26.986 --> 34:29.119
- We talked about
how much the liberals hate us,

34:29.163 --> 34:31.121
how stupid they think we are.

34:31.165 --> 34:33.428
If I dare to express a view
contrary to theirs,

34:33.471 --> 34:37.040
I'm an idiot,
a racist, homophobic...

34:37.084 --> 34:39.477
I mean, this is America.

34:39.521 --> 34:40.913
We should be able
to express our views

34:40.957 --> 34:42.828
without being attacked.

34:42.872 --> 34:44.787
- Did you discuss
anything else?

34:44.830 --> 34:46.397
- Yes.

34:46.441 --> 34:47.790
The New York Knicks.

34:47.833 --> 34:51.228
- Ha.
[chuckles]

34:51.272 --> 34:55.145
Did Jordan Reed ask you
or Manny Lopez

34:55.189 --> 34:57.452
to commit an act of violence,

34:57.495 --> 35:01.238
to help protect the country
against the liberal cabal?

35:01.282 --> 35:02.935
- No, sir.

35:05.155 --> 35:06.417
- Nothing further.

35:08.202 --> 35:09.638
- You weren't standing
next to Manny Lopez

35:09.681 --> 35:10.813
the whole night, correct?

35:10.856 --> 35:12.162
- Correct.
- You weren't standing

35:12.206 --> 35:13.859
next to Jordan Reed
the whole night either?

35:13.903 --> 35:15.557
- Correct.
- So it's possible

35:15.600 --> 35:17.602
Manny Lopez and Jordan Reed may
have discussed something else

35:17.646 --> 35:20.127
including committing
acts of violence, correct?

35:20.170 --> 35:22.303
- It's possible, but--
- This wasn't the only

35:22.346 --> 35:24.261
political event Mr. Reed
ever sponsored, correct?

35:24.305 --> 35:26.524
- No.
He puts on lots of rallies.

35:26.568 --> 35:28.091
Once a week, actually.

35:28.135 --> 35:31.616
[dramatic music]

35:31.660 --> 35:33.662
- How'd you find out
about these rallies?

35:33.705 --> 35:34.880
- Word of mouth, mostly.

35:34.924 --> 35:36.447
People usually text each other.

35:36.491 --> 35:38.188
♪

35:38.232 --> 35:39.668
- Thank you.
Nothing further.

35:39.711 --> 35:41.757
♪

35:41.800 --> 35:43.324
Get a subpoena
for Pond's phone.

35:43.367 --> 35:46.196
We need to review his texts
then do a deep dive

35:46.240 --> 35:47.850
into every rally
Reed's attended

35:47.893 --> 35:49.286
for the past few months.

35:49.330 --> 35:52.071
Then have detectives scrub
the surveillance footage.

35:52.115 --> 35:55.118
We need a clip,
a quote, a sound bite,

35:55.162 --> 35:57.729
something that reveals
who Jordan Reed really is.

35:57.773 --> 36:00.645
- Happy to do it, but why?

36:00.689 --> 36:02.081
- Excuse me?

36:02.125 --> 36:04.083
- We rested our case
two days ago.

36:04.127 --> 36:05.868
Even if we find
something interesting,

36:05.911 --> 36:07.217
we can't introduce it.

36:07.261 --> 36:09.219
- But we can use it on cross.

36:09.263 --> 36:10.916
- Once again,
happy to do it,

36:10.960 --> 36:12.309
but there is no indication

36:12.353 --> 36:14.311
that Reed is actually
going to testify.

36:14.355 --> 36:17.140
- You really think the biggest
media whore in America

36:17.184 --> 36:19.534
is gonna pass up the
opportunity to wrap himself

36:19.577 --> 36:20.752
in the First Amendment,

36:20.796 --> 36:22.580
and provide free content

36:22.624 --> 36:24.060
for his media company?

36:24.103 --> 36:25.279
Not a chance.

36:25.322 --> 36:27.890
Get the subpoena,
and start scrubbing.

36:27.933 --> 36:32.721
♪

36:32.764 --> 36:37.900
- Have you spent any time in
a chat room called Rogue Wave?

36:37.943 --> 36:39.075
- I'm aware of it,

36:39.118 --> 36:42.078
but I've actually
never participated

36:42.121 --> 36:45.299
in any online discussions.

36:45.342 --> 36:48.084
Like I said, we have over
500 employees at the company,

36:48.127 --> 36:50.260
and most of them
are very patriotic too.

36:50.304 --> 36:53.394
So it's possible one of them
might have used my computer.

36:53.437 --> 36:54.830
- Mm-hmm.

36:54.873 --> 36:56.092
Nothing further.

36:58.137 --> 36:59.226
- You ready?

37:02.490 --> 37:04.796
Highly unusual
for an employee

37:04.840 --> 37:07.103
to use the CEO's office
without his knowledge

37:07.146 --> 37:08.757
or permission, correct?

37:08.800 --> 37:10.062
- Not at my company.

37:10.106 --> 37:12.195
We have an open
and inclusive culture.

37:12.239 --> 37:13.283
Doors are never closed.

37:13.327 --> 37:14.763
In fact, most offices

37:14.806 --> 37:16.155
don't even have doors.

37:16.199 --> 37:18.201
- Your office has a door.
- Yes.

37:18.245 --> 37:21.987
But I never close it
or lock it.

37:22.031 --> 37:23.859
- Your computer has a password,
correct?

37:23.902 --> 37:25.643
- It does, yes,
but it's written

37:25.687 --> 37:27.906
on one of those
yellow sticky things

37:27.950 --> 37:28.994
stuck to the computer.

37:29.038 --> 37:31.083
It's...
it's low-tech, I know,

37:31.127 --> 37:33.303
but I'm always forgetting
my damn passwords.

37:33.347 --> 37:36.611
You know, too many devices
and subscriptions...

37:36.654 --> 37:39.657
- You said it earlier a lot of
your employees are patriotic.

37:39.701 --> 37:41.224
You consider yourself
a patriot too?

37:41.268 --> 37:42.443
- Yes, of course.

37:42.486 --> 37:44.314
- I imagine you
also consider yourself

37:44.358 --> 37:46.447
a proud proponent
of the First Amendment.

37:46.490 --> 37:47.317
- I do.

37:47.361 --> 37:49.928
Freedom of speech is

37:49.972 --> 37:52.453
the cornerstone
of our democracy.

37:52.496 --> 37:56.195
It's the defining feature
of our country.

37:56.239 --> 37:59.198
People have the right
to express

37:59.242 --> 38:01.375
their religious
and political beliefs

38:01.418 --> 38:03.246
even if they're unpopular,

38:03.290 --> 38:07.076
even if the people in power
find them abhorrent,

38:07.119 --> 38:09.905
and that open exchange
right there,

38:09.948 --> 38:13.343
that is what makes America
the greatest country on Earth.

38:13.387 --> 38:16.172
- So your goal was to foster

38:16.215 --> 38:19.349
the open exchange
of opinions and ideas?

38:19.393 --> 38:22.744
- Yes, I just wanna give
patriotic Americans a forum

38:22.787 --> 38:24.659
to express their thoughts.

38:24.702 --> 38:27.836
You know, contrary
to popular opinion, Mr. Price,

38:27.879 --> 38:30.795
most conservatives don't enjoy
the didactic rhetoric

38:30.839 --> 38:32.275
of the far-left.

38:32.319 --> 38:35.365
- So despite the outrageous
and inflammatory posts

38:35.409 --> 38:37.672
sent from your office computer,

38:37.715 --> 38:39.108
your goal was simply

38:39.151 --> 38:42.067
to cultivate
a peaceful exchange of ideas?

38:42.111 --> 38:43.678
- Yes.
- You didn't want

38:43.721 --> 38:45.723
your followers
to commit acts of violence?

38:45.767 --> 38:47.290
- No, no, no.

38:47.334 --> 38:49.423
No, that would be
the last thing I'd ever want.

38:52.034 --> 38:54.210
- I'd like to show you
a video clip of you talking

38:54.253 --> 38:56.647
to one of your employees
at a recent rally--

38:56.691 --> 38:59.128
- Objection.
We haven't had a chance

38:59.171 --> 39:00.564
to review this material.

39:00.608 --> 39:02.392
- There was no reason
to share it until now.

39:02.436 --> 39:04.568
We couldn't anticipate
the defendant would testify,

39:04.612 --> 39:08.006
and open the door with his
statements about cultivating

39:08.050 --> 39:10.574
the peaceful exchange of ideas.

39:10.618 --> 39:13.142
- And this video clip
will rebut those statements?

39:13.185 --> 39:15.405
- It will directly contradict
what the defendant just said

39:15.449 --> 39:19.061
regarding his goals
and objectives.

39:19.104 --> 39:20.497
- I'll allow it.

39:25.807 --> 39:27.417
- Look at these idiots,

39:27.461 --> 39:29.593
drinkin',
gettin' all riled up.

39:31.900 --> 39:34.076
If we could just find a way
to activate these morons

39:34.119 --> 39:35.338
to actually attack

39:35.382 --> 39:37.645
or even kill

39:37.688 --> 39:40.909
some trans-bathroom-loving
liberal,

39:40.952 --> 39:43.868
we--

39:43.912 --> 39:46.784
we'd be the number one
media company in the world.

39:46.828 --> 39:48.569
[dramatic music]

39:48.612 --> 39:49.961
[chuckles]

39:50.005 --> 39:54.357
♪

39:54.401 --> 39:58.187
- A waiter took that video
at a recent rally.

39:58.230 --> 40:02.452
It shows you saying you'd like
to see one of "these morons"

40:02.496 --> 40:05.237
attack or kill someone.

40:05.281 --> 40:09.285
- I was kidding.
Come on, that--I was joking.

40:09.328 --> 40:11.243
- That's a hell of a thing
to joke about.

40:11.287 --> 40:17.032
♪

40:17.075 --> 40:18.207
Nothing further.

40:18.250 --> 40:19.687
♪

40:19.730 --> 40:20.818
- Defense?

40:20.862 --> 40:22.341
- Nothing at this time.

40:22.385 --> 40:28.217
♪

40:28.260 --> 40:30.219
- Has the jury
reached a verdict?

40:30.262 --> 40:31.699
- We have, Your Honor.

40:31.742 --> 40:33.483
On the count
of Murder in the Second Degree,

40:33.527 --> 40:35.137
we find the defendant...

40:35.180 --> 40:37.748
guilty.
- [laughs]

40:37.792 --> 40:39.707
You've got to be--

40:39.750 --> 40:42.187
get off of me.

40:42.231 --> 40:44.494
This isn't over.
This isn't over!

40:44.538 --> 40:47.279
The true patriots
will have the last say.

40:47.323 --> 40:49.238
They will not stand
for this act of tyranny!

40:49.281 --> 40:52.502
♪

40:52.546 --> 40:53.982
- Hell of a verdict, Nolan.

40:54.025 --> 40:56.854
Will make people think twice
before tweeting venom.

40:56.898 --> 40:58.073
- I'm not so sure.

40:58.116 --> 41:00.554
Someone called
"garrett-from-the-country"

41:00.597 --> 41:03.121
just tweeted me a particularly
venomous death threat.

41:03.165 --> 41:08.779
♪

41:12.566 --> 41:12.783
.

41:12.827 --> 41:15.743
[dramatic music]

41:15.786 --> 41:22.706
♪

41:32.324 --> 41:39.462
♪

41:42.073 --> 41:44.989
[wolf howls]
